705084f-a.title: Brooklyn: Jamaica Avenue - Vermont Avenue
705084f-a.text:
Jamaica Ave., north side, west of Vermont Ave., showing the 4-story
Schmidt Brewery (1912) marked J.B. 1898; beyond it is L. Breitkopf's Hotel.
(1912).
April 1929.
Eugene I. Armbruster Collection.
